00:11:53.171 --> 00:11:55.590 position:50% align:center
You think a 31-year-old
would know?

00:11:55.674 --> 00:11:58.134 position:50% align:center
[KUMATANI] I'd say there's
a bear-y good chance.

00:11:58.218 --> 00:11:59.511 position:50% align:center
[GIRL F]
Thanks!

00:12:01.971 --> 00:12:05.141 position:50% align:center
[GIRL F] Uramichi Oniisan,
what does "servile" mean?

00:12:05.225 --> 00:12:09.938 position:50% align:center
[URAMICHI] It means...
you try to do what people want.

00:12:10.021 --> 00:12:12.440 position:50% align:center
