00:13:46.993 --> 00:13:48.411 position:50% align:center
and society and
authority might have

00:13:48.495 --> 00:13:50.497 position:50% align:center
ground his soul down to a stump,

00:13:50.580 --> 00:13:52.749 position:50% align:center
but being a gymnast Oniisan
on a children's show

00:13:52.832 --> 00:13:54.334 position:50% align:center
really means something to him,

00:13:54.417 --> 00:13:57.087 position:50% align:center
so he fights to keep what's
left of his conscience,

00:13:57.170 --> 00:13:59.714 position:50% align:center
for the kids' sake.

00:13:59.798 --> 00:14:03.593 position:50% align:center
Uramichi, I know
I'm mostly just guessing,

00:14:03.677 --> 00:14:07.472 position:50% align:center
